      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $5,900, this vehicle is being sold as a poor-condition example and should be approached as a project, fixer-upper, or possible parts car depending on your plans. It shows significant age and wear, and buyers should expect cosmetic flaws, interior wear, and mechanical needs rather than a clean, ready-to-enjoy driver. It may still have usable value for the right person, but it will need attention and money to bring up to a more dependable or presentable standard. Best suited for someone who knows what they are looking at and is comfortable taking on repairs.",
