      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward value for someone seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains an accessible way into ownership at an appealing price point. A sensible choice for buyers who prioritize affordability and opportunity.",
