    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right owner? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option that could make a great runaround, project, or first car for someone handy. It starts conversations for all the right reasons: approachable price, practical potential, and a straightforward sale from someone who believes in being upfront. If you want inexpensive motoring without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
