    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project candidate with solid bones and plenty of usable life for the right buyer. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels like a workable platform for a budget daily, shop truck, or weekend revival. Cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and needed repairs are present, so it\u2019s best approached as a fixer or value-minded driver, but there\u2019s real upside here for someone who knows their way around maintenance. Priced to move and well worth a look if you want an affordable entry point.",
